    title: "Warehouse Construction Cost Per Square Foot (2026 Guide)",
    slug: "warehouse-construction-cost-per-square-foot-2026",
    excerpt: "Current warehouse construction costs in the Charlotte region broken down by building type, size, and features — from basic storage shells to climate-controlled distribution centers.",
    date: "2026-05-08",
